Install instructions from http://docs.puppetlabs.com/guides/installation.html#mac-os-x

* Download dmg's
  - puppet
  - hiera
  - factor
* hdiutils attach /path/to/dmg
* sudo installer -pkg /Volumes/volume-0.0.0/volume-0.0.0.pkg -target /
* puppet resource group puppet ensure=present
* puppet resource user puppet ensure=present gid=puppet shell='/sbin/nologin'
